                 Windows  MongoDB deployments can use _-_-_l_d_a_p_B_i_n_d_W_i_t_h_O_S_D_e_f_a_u_l_t_s
                 instead of _-_-_l_d_a_p_Q_u_e_r_y_U_s_e_r and _-_-_l_d_a_p_Q_u_e_r_y_P_a_s_s_w_o_r_d. You  can‐
                 not specify both _-_-_l_d_a_p_Q_u_e_r_y_U_s_e_r and _-_-_l_d_a_p_B_i_n_d_W_i_t_h_O_S_D_e_f_a_u_l_t_s
                 at the same time.

       ----llddaappQQuueerryyPPaasssswwoorrdd <<ssttrriinngg>>
