              _-_-_l_d_a_p_Q_u_e_r_y_U_s_e_r.   You   must   use   _-_-_l_d_a_p_Q_u_e_r_y_P_a_s_s_w_o_r_d   with
              _-_-_l_d_a_p_Q_u_e_r_y_U_s_e_r.

