                         │Value      │ Description                │
                         ├───────────┼────────────────────────────┤
                         │ddiissaabblleedd   │ The  server  does  not use │
                         │           │ TLS/SSL.                   │
                         ├───────────┼────────────────────────────┤
                         │aalllloowwSSSSLL   │ Connections        between │
                         │           │ servers    do    not   use │
                         │           │ TLS/SSL. For incoming con‐ │
                         │           │ nections,    the    server │
                         │           │ accepts both  TLS/SSL  and │
                         │           │ non-TLS/non-SSL.           │
                         ├───────────┼────────────────────────────┤
                         │pprreeffeerrSSSSLL  │ Connections        between │
                         │           │ servers use  TLS/SSL.  For │
                         │           │ incoming  connections, the │
                         │           │ server    accepts     both │
                         │           │ TLS/SSL                and │
                         │           │ non-TLS/non-SSL.           │
                         ├───────────┼────────────────────────────┤
                         │rreeqquuiirreeSSSSLL │ The   server   uses    and │
                         │           │ accepts    only    TLS/SSL │
                         │           │ encrypted connections.     │
                         └───────────┴────────────────────────────┘

              Starting in version 3.4, if ----ssssllCCAAFFiillee  or  ssssll..CCAAFFiillee  is  not
