              specified unless using _-_-_s_s_l_C_e_r_t_i_f_i_c_a_t_e_S_e_l_e_c_t_o_r.

              For more information  about  TLS/SSL  and  MongoDB,  see  /tuto‐
              rial/configure-ssl and /tutorial/configure-ssl-clients .

